    "mc_patrol_image_text": {
      "type": "mc_patrol-image-text",
      "blocks": {
        "slide_1": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "pc_image": "shopify://shop_images/patrol-param-text-image1-new.jpg",
            "image_position": "left",
            "title": "<p><strong>52V 30AH</strong> Removable Battery</p>",
            "title_color": "#ffffff",
            "title_bold_color": "#ffe500",
            "title_gradient_color": "",
            "text": "<p>Equipped with a <strong>1560Wh (52V 30Ah) </strong>battery, the Patrol delivers up to 50 miles of range for demanding off-road rides. The removable design allows easy charging anywhere, while 15–80% fast charging in just <strong>3.5 hours</strong> means less waiting and more riding.</p>",
            "text_color": "#747474"
          }
        },
        "slide_2": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "pc_image": "shopify://shop_images/patrol-param-text-image2-new.jpg",
            "image_position": "right",
            "title": "<p><strong>Superior </strong>Suspension</p>",
            "title_color": "#ffffff",
            "title_bold_color": "#ffe500",
            "title_gradient_color": "",
            "text": "<p>Built for rugged terrain, the Patrol combines a <strong>150 mm long-travel hydraulic front fork with lockout and a rear hydraulic shock</strong> to absorb hard hits and rough trails. The full-suspension setup enhances stability and traction, giving you better control and a smoother ride across dirt, rocks, and uneven ground.</p>",
            "text_color": "#747474"
          }
        },
        "slide_3": {
          "type": "slide",
          "settings": {
            "pc_image": "shopify://shop_images/patrol-param-text-image3-new.jpg",
            "image_position": "left",
            "title": "<p>Smart <strong>NFC </strong>Access</p>",
            "title_color": "#ffffff",
            "title_bold_color": "#ffe500",
            "title_gradient_color": "",
            "text": "<p>The Patrol is equipped with an <strong>NFC card access system</strong> for fast and secure bike activation. Simply tap the card to power on—no physical keys required. This intelligent system enhances security while providing a seamless and convenient riding experience.</p>",
            "text_color": "#747474"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "slide_1",
        "slide_2",
        "slide_3"
      ],
